Here is a simple Web VR world called "DudeWorld" using A-Frame. This implementation starts with 10 randomly colored cubes randomly placed in the scene. The entire setup is contained in a single HTML file, which includes embedded CSS and JavaScript.

### Complete HTML Code:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DudeWorld VR</title>
    <script src="https://aframe.io/releases/1.2.0/aframe.min.js"></script>
